    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This naturally aspirated power plant utilizes six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS to provide a broad torque curve and an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain consists of a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox delivering power to the rear wheels via a mechanical limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The chassis dynamics remain sharp with refreshed bushings and a well-sorted suspension geometry, offering the tactile feedback and lateral stability expected of this platform. This is a driver-focused example with excellent mechanical compression and a clean power delivery profile.",
